title: ICEnroll2::get_EnableT61DNEncoding (xenroll.h)
description: The EnableT61DNEncoding property of ICEnroll4 sets or retrieves a Boolean value that determines whether the distinguished name in the request is encoded as a T61 string instead of as a Unicode string. (Get)
